The National Housing Authority (NHA) shall transfer, at no cost, title and ownership of the aforementioned parcels of land to the Republic of the Philippines and deliver title thereof to Parks and Wildlife Division, DENR, which is charged with management and administration thereof.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF , I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

Done in the City of Manila, this 25th day of October in the year of Our Lord, Two Thousand and Four.

( Sgd .) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: ( Sgd .) EDUARDO R. ERMITA Executive Secretary

